#Text= Aye - aye spirit says : " You are not welcome in my oasis , human .

column1: #Text=I 'm starving and I have n't slept all night .
#Text=" Aye - aye spirit says : " Not my problem .
#Text=" Aye - aye spirit says : " You dare use fire against me ?
#Text=" Aye - aye spirit says : " And who might you be ?
#Text=" Wan says : " I am Bushy , the Bush Spirit .
#Text=And I would like the enter your oasis .
#Text=" Aye - aye spirit says : " Very well .
#Text=" Wan says : " Come on , let me in , just for a little while .
#Text=" Wan says : " Believe me , I 'd love to go back home .
#Text=" Friendly spirit # 1 says : " That 's too bad .
#Text=" Aye - aye spirit says : " Do n't pity him .
#Text=He 's just like every other human : ugly , destructive , and lacking any respect for nature .
#Text=" Wan says : " Who are you calling ugly , Ugly ?
#Text=" Friendly spirit # 1 says : " If you ca n't go back to your city , then you should go live in another one .
#Text=" Aye - aye spirit says : " " There are other lion turtles ? "
#Text=Of course there are , dozens of them !
#Text=" Wan says : " So which way to the nearest lion turtle city ?
#Text=I think it 's on the other side of none - of - your - business valley .
#Text=I 'm gon na get you out of there .
